OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNY police to pay $17.5m    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fover hijab mugshot row     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, New York's police department is to pay 
OL,6, $17.5m (#14m) in a class action case   
OL,7, led by two Muslim women who were forced
OL,8, to remove their hijabs while having    
OL,9, mugshots taken.                        
OL,11,FThe 2018 case argued that Jamilla Clark
OL,12,Fand Arwa Aziz suffered violations of   
OL,13,Freligious freedom and privacy.         
OL,15,FLawyers say more than 3,600 people are 
OL,16,Feligible for pay-outs under the deal.  
OL,18,FPolice policy changed four years ago to
OL,19,Fallow hijabs. The city said the case   
OL,20,Fhad "resulted in a positive reform".   
